content:
Fish may refer to a number of topics:

  • Fish caught using the Fishing skill
  • Fishing is a skill used to catch edible sea creatures and other items
  • Fishing items are useful items concerned with fishing, including a list of fish that players can catch
  • Several types of fish found underwater on Fossil Island or at the Mogre Camp:
    • Fish (angelfish)
    • Fish (black moor fantail)
    • Fish (discus)
    • Fish (harlequin)
    • Fish (neon tetra)
    • Fish (paradise)
    • Fish (pearl danio)
    • Fish (red fantail)
  • Fresh Fish, an item used to gain Piscarilius favour.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
